"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'宋体\'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:600; background-color:#ffff00;\">还债</span><span style=\" font-family:\'宋体\'; font-size:12pt;\">：俚语。上面这位玩家，假设他又继续扫出了一局</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman,serif\'; font-size:12pt;\">42.77</span><span style=\" font-family:\'宋体\'; font-size:12pt;\">（</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman,serif\'; font-size:12pt;\">43</span><span style=\" font-family:\'宋体\'; font-size:12pt;\">）那么这个时候就可以说他把</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman,serif\'; font-size:12pt;\">43</span><span style=\" font-family:\'宋体\'; font-size:12pt;\">秒给还上了，这叫还债。</span> </p>\n"
